{"tid":986403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】前日警察拉左五毛岳不群個老母","createTime":"2019-01-18T11:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T04:28:21.000Z","uid":54337,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bad39acb5c0bde0e6f26b6c23c070d77f23740f3","tid":986403,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"跨部門油尖區掃黃 34內地女被捕<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Ufld9kdgf6plUZmBe%2FWzNjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b0577d6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】油尖警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，昨日(16日)傍晚約6時，展開代號「烽火」(FIRESTORM)的掃黃行動，突擊搜查油麻地砵蘭街、咸美頓街、碧街、窩打老道、廟街、上海街及尖沙咀一帶的多個單位及酒店，拘捕共34名內地女子（17至65歲），其中30人持雙程證，其餘4人持護照，她們涉嫌違反逗留條件，現正被扣留調查，稍後將交由入境事務處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X217ujPME7HiuU_znMsPXA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ny4wMjU2NDEwMjU2NDEwNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/sKjqBOOlAOJys.1YaoPUvg--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/ad6cb79b7bea8a4a58b07e5016729a2d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FX217ujPME7HiuU_znMsPXA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ny4wMjU2NDEwMjU2NDEwNQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsKjqBOOlAOJys.1YaoPUvg--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fad6cb79b7bea8a4a58b07e5016729a2d&h=c3a1176c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9c84af923f08194417a3642863347e0618dd02a","tid":986403,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"65歲老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84abbf7b22ed60a6ea6b307a679acd84c5edced","tid":986403,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b9c84af923f08194417a3642863347e0618dd02a","tid":986403,"uid":171107,"l